channel.title: How do i start playing moparscape?
channel.description: Can some one tell me how to play mopar scape? Because I don't know how to get in. The guy who made it should have user accounts for people to log in with their own user name and password. And please don't delete this post!

download moparscape from www.moparisthebest.com Or use the client on the page. then when you’ve downloaded it click on the server status page from www.moparisthebest.com and choose one of the online servers. hope i helped.
